    DeviceInit:


        · Listview  - This listview only  shows the device name  without further
                      information.  This is  only for  orientation in  a bulk of
                      devices.




    DeviceInit/Page1:


        · Init string   - The  string  that  should  be  sent  to  the device at
                          startup.

        · Out string    - The string sent to the  modem when shuting  down elCID
                          (elCIDSerial).

        · Dial string   - Not used  in this release.  In future you  specify the
                          dial prefix.




