    DeviceInit/Page2:


        · Reject string             - The  string  that  causes  the  device  to
                                      reject a call.

        · Global reject string      - String  that  causes the device  to reject
                                      ALL calls. (n/a) $$$

        · Global reject off string  - The  string  that  turns  off  global call
                                      rejecting. (n/a) $$$




