    MSNs:

        · Listview  - Here you see an overview of your configured MSNs.

        · Name      - The name of the selected entry.

        · MSN       - The configured MultiSubscriberNumber.

        · Location  - The location the MSN is configured for.


        · Add       - Pressing  this button will  add a "» New «"  entry to  the
