@NODE "elCIDPrefs\Phonebook" "elCID V2.2 · elCIDPrefs\Phonebook"
@NEXT "elCIDPrefs\DisplayFormat"
@PREV "elCIDPrefs\MSNs"
@TITLE "elCID V2.2 · elCIDPrefs\Phonebook"


    Phonebook:

        This is the place where you configure the name, address and phone number
        of all your friends and others.
        There  are  two entries called "» Anonymous «" and "» Unknown «".  These
        entries used for calls which are not recognised by number (anonymous) or
        currently  unknown  to the phonebook.  All other calls will be processed
        according to the extracted phonenumber.


