        · Name      - The name of the selected entry.


        · Edit      - Pressing  this button let you edit the selected entry.

        · Add       - Pressing  this button will  add a "» New «"  entry to  the
                      list.

        · Del       - Deletes an old entry without warning.

        · Sort      - You can sort the phonebook list by pressing this button.




        When  adding  or  editing  (doubleclick)  entries, another window called
        "Phonebook edit"  will  be opened.  If you  select  one  of the  special
        entries,  the  "Action"  page  will  be  shown and the "General" page is
        disabled.


