    Phonebook/Edit/General:

        Should i explain these?? Ok!


        · Forename  - The forename of the person.

        · Surname   - The last name of the person.

        · Street    - The street the person lives in.

        · ZIP       - The ZIP code.

        · City      - The city the person lives in.

        · Phone     - Phone number of that person.

        · Info      - Some information about this person.




